int a = 10;
    int *p = &a;
cout << p<<endl;
it gives the value stored at p 

 below from CHAT GPT
| Loop type                 | Use                                   |
| ------------------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| `for (int i=0; i<n; i++)` | ✅ input + index access                |
| `for (int x : arr)`       | ❌ not for input (only reading values) |


